 7.CREAYTE VIEW ----creating view name as students_details that specifiies some special column from employee table 


  a.  CREATE VIEW STUDENT_DETAILS AS
    SELECT ID, NAME, MOBILE
    FROM STUDENTS
    WHERE CLASS = "A";

B. drop a view 


   DROP VIEW STUDENT_DETAILS;







